Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"When Zeus commanded"'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"the people who lived on the land\Nlearned to plant seeds and till the soil."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, your pronunciation\Nis wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm trying to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotten better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first came here, I thought\Nthat you were a terrible student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to\Nthat Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's traveling\Naround the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see him once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've started working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So what kind of work is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an interior decorator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see ! You probably have\Nquite a good eye for furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interiors, but it's a little\Ndifferent from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a kitchen designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny, isn't it? I've never even\Nstood in a kitchen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you do\Nmy kitchen sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But your kitchens\Nmust fetch quite a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been drinking,\Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we rush, the day will pass and\Ntomorrow will come in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happiness is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired of hearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was happy just because\NI was waiting for him at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That man called Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,People are strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Their sadness slowly fades and\Nleaves only the fun memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People sure are\Ndesigned conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can\Nkeep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Verdemann, the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the person who cleared\Nyour name, Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up as much\Nas I could about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You graduated from\N511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a secret agent\Nfor East Germany and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,traveled around the world\Nposing as a freelance journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you investigated\Nhuman rights violations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as a freelance journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain of data in your big bag\Nwas evidence of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only thing we never learned\Nwas your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He left without\Ntelling us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer an inspector,\NDetective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you became\Na professor at a police academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I converse regularly\Nwith my daughter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I say converse,\Nbut it's by email.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent our lives as parent and child\Nwithout telling each other anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We both lived our lives not knowing\Nanything about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How many things can\Npeople say in a lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably had a lot he wanted\Nto talk about over a good beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back\Nto Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The company I'm under\Ncontract with is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?\NA lot happened to you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's pointless to run away."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's important is to\Nface the truth and move on."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you dispose of this\Nwhen you have the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen and\NI will always help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter and "him", too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Questioning continues for Dr. Tenma.\NThe case in its entirety is still unclear."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Inspector Lunge's\Ntestimony begins."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Could this possibly be the worst\Nserial murder case in European history?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma\Ncompletely innocent."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"The police formally\Napologize to Dr. Tenma."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"A motive for the case\Nstill has not been found."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is the mysterious young man\Nwho is the supposed real criminal?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"The University Münster's\Nmedical department"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"invites Dr. Tenma to\Nbecome a professor."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma declines firmly."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma joins\NDoctors Without Borders."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The articles get\Nsmaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People are designed\Nconveniently, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dieter, you've gotten bigger\Nsince the last time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heckel, it looks like you've\Ngotten sneakier since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a chatty brat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't hang around.\NI've got soccer practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Tenma come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He joined Doctors Without Borders,\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to look good by doing\Nsomething that doesn't make any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get a hold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nif he is back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the expenses\NI incurred and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the labor I put into that job\Nhe gave me a little while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he\Ncompensated me enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma gave you a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he was\Njust looking for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was a lot of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to steal confidential\Ninformation from the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what'll happen\Nif they catch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Tenma this bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can't pay it I'm going to make him\Nbecome an underground doctor again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.\NYou haven't come for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, share this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is nice.\NMany leaves are photosynthesizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Life. .. Countless genes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of Mendel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he discovered\Nthe rules of genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the same university\Nas Mendel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno University.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in a city in Moravia, the Czech\NRepublic's southeastern region.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go there some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming by so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enjoyed the times\Nwe spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can\Ntell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something you\Nwant to ask me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the mother of the twins,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That man killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was that\Nman's experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forgive that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, these children growing\Ninside me will definitely punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of my hand.\NMy hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the real monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children are still alive,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I may never\Nremember it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave those children names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Their names are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tardy, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ten minutes late\Nfor our appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Professor Kronecker...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Its fine. You know why\NI called you in today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about\Nyour graduation thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that a lot\Nhas happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be pretty difficult to catch up\Nafter your absence from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But that isn't an excuse\Nfor my grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now about your thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best thesis I have\Nreceived from any of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! A lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that you will be able to\Nsave many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be allowed to be late\Nfor court, Fräulein Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, are you graduating?\NI'll be here with you even if you aren't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how reliable you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you cheer me up\Nthe next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can tell from your voice\Nthat you're just acting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did it.\NCongratulations!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Things will get\Ntougher from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's celebrate.\NCome home quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have a lot planned\Nwith my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you talking about?!\NTenma's coming back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just got a call.{\i0}
